yBwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=6b17167c\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20151202/00180_012.html</a><br />\n<br />\n咁又唔好話你啊媽on9<br />\n外國有人試過因為對wifi電磁過敏而自殺死咗<br />\n去問下佢有咩唔舒服先啦"},{"pid":"4b46bc389a553d71ae684d9d07ac46538df1dcc4","tid":57164,"uid":43483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T22:59:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢近排on9到臨訓收埋個router<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我條寬頻線係廳(唯一無左router都上到網個條)，我又拉唔到入房。有無方法係我唔洗連router可以上到網？ homeplug係咪有用？點用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20151202/00180_012.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20151202%2F00180_012.html&d=DVWoahwgonv%2FIpZBhWpyBwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=6b17167c\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20151202/00180_012.html</a><br />\n<br />\n咁又唔好話你啊媽on9<br />\n外國有人試過因為對wifi電磁過敏而自殺死咗<br />\n去問下佢有咩唔舒服先啦</blockquote><br />\n香港周街都係Wi-Fi<br />\n剩係熄樓主個router 就無事心理作用居多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係就扮哂野唔想樓主上網夜訓搵借口姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca39905c8bea857243e31788e5d1a7b14fa88768","tid":57164,"uid":8274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T23:12:26.000Z","msg":"啲上左年紀既人<br />\n一對於睇唔到既野，就好鐘意怪力亂神，用自己方法演繹，你問佢乜野係 wifi 佢又口擘擘答你唔到，但就係要言之鑿鑿咁講自己套理論<br />\n呢種論調真係好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nWifi signal 強度低到不得了，低過佢開住電話<br />\n而且住香港，到到都十鳩幾萬個wifi 射住，根本心理作用<br />\n你唔好俾佢知原來佢瞓果陣原來仲有咁多個 wifi 射住佢，佢心理作用咁勁，呢世都唔洗瞓，一到夜晚喊苦喊忽又會落管理處投訴人地影響鄰居又剩<br />\n或者是要搬去深山"},{"pid":"aa1db9216c80fa3b738492f2d50aafaa81052f83","tid":57164,"uid":47128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T23:26:57.000Z","msg":"失眠多數心理因素大d<br />\n唔好成日疑神疑鬼好過"},{"pid":"1d0860f132a1ea262a1d18e7b7aadb0c38bc971b","tid":57164,"uid":7758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T23:43:24.000Z","msg":"自己買過隻router然後 disable ssid broadcast"},{"pid":"b05d41bbfebc544d0741bf68f575fd8a02328b04","tid":57164,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T23:46:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbcf7b7332c18c1d8772b8900764bf31634392e7","tid":57164,"uid":49260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T23:53:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> wifi 真係會影響睡眠嫁on9"},{"pid":"035eb144f7c5370d044a42a3df6982663f28973c","tid":57164,"uid":4209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T23:55:50.000Z","msg":"連router都比人搶埋，咁撚廢架<br />\n<br />\n佢唔比你打機咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cdff3b76b542362bfc47b429dcc22e35bcd8d18","tid":57164,"uid":2781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T00:16:05.000Z","msg":"買條長啲嘅lan"},{"pid":"8e4734891b4e0536ed7240ea08f7d3a3eb8a3e0b","tid":57164,"uid":742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T00:24:39.000Z","msg":"天下老母一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n苦主<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5e8110e723e283629ed0fcb4b2211184850aa1","tid":57164,"uid":34990,"like":0